7 and 26, 1931, appeared on October 20 in the émigré daily Poslednie Novosti, Paris, and was included in the collection Soglyadatay, Russkiya Zapiski, Paris, 1938.

V.N., Details of a Sunset and Other Stories, 1976





TERRA INCOGNITA


The Russian original of “Terra Incognita” appeared under the same title in Poslednie Novosti, Paris, November 22, 1931, and was reprinted in my collection Soglyadatay, Paris, 1938. The present English translation was published in The New Yorker, May 18, 19